<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٩٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5442">ابْنُ أَبِي عَدِيٍّ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1513">حُصَيْنٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2238">سَالِمٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا إِذَا صَعِدْنَا كَبَّرْنَا وَإِذَا تَصَوَّبْنَا سَبَّحْنَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>